-- Metlife to buy back up to $1 billion shares
-- By Amrutha Gayathri in Bangalore
-- Tue Jun 10, 2014 06:29AM EDT
-- None



June 10 (Reuters) - Insurer Metlife Inc <MET.N> said it would buy back up to $1 billion of its common stock.

The company said it will use existing authorizations from its board for the share repurchase. [ID:nBw8vtBCxa]